<< -what clearance should the valves be set at?>>

Hi Michael,
.004", but in weather warmer than 70F it might be a good idea to adjust them 
for .005" ot .006" to compensate for any valve stretch when running hot.

<< -do I clamp or weld my muffler tip on?  >>

